    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386200/extras/362a468bec8b89033917e080c313ef4a.avif?t=1771881161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386200/extras_big/362a468bec8b89033917e080c313ef4a.webp?t=1771881161 width=1560 height=203 /></span>PSI 是一款以移动机制为核心的攀爬游戏。你背负着一个没有退路的使命，只为拯救一个濒临毁灭的两栖货物崇拜部族。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386200/extras/560793abe510e7ff5b8106df5574afcc.poster.avif?t=1771881161\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386200/extras/560793abe510e7ff5b8106df5574afcc.webm?t=1771881161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386200/extras/560793abe510e7ff5b8106df5574afcc.mp4?t=1771881161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386200/extras/0583ed0b8dcb86aac5e4c829cd239de9.avif?t=1771881161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386200/extras_big/0583ed0b8dcb86aac5e4c829cd239de9.webp?t=1771881161 width=1560 height=203 /></span>利用喷气背包，在地下水电网络的高墙之间穿梭跳跃！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386200/extras/39c5a93e0b9459948675aa7680fe655a.poster.avif?t=1771881161\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386200/extras/39c5a93e0b9459948675